_Hif’il_ Future Tense: The _hif’il_ binyan has a [[future tense]], which is one of the [[Hif’il Forms|forms of the _hif’il_ binyan]].
- The _hif’il_ future tense has [[_Hif’il_ Future Tense for regular shorushim|conjugations for regular shorushim]].
- The _hif’il_ future tense has forms for irregular shorushim which will be added at a later time.
